steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT035FlatListPreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT035FlatListPreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT035FlatListPreviewCode
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT035FlatListPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I add item "FlatList" without inputting in Search popup to preview mobile editor
When I open preview code with component mode
Then I should see the code content "M3501_MAIN_FLATLIST_INIT"
